{"tid":871482,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個出街對付支那人既方法","createTime":"2018-10-22T03:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T14:24:22.000Z","uid":82521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"699de8b7cf08d98dffa08893acd0cbe3d3a11ed9","tid":871482,"uid":82521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:33:18.000Z","msg":"平時返工要周圍去 今次比公司掟咗返尖沙咀<br />\n返工已經燥到仆街 比啲支那人阻住條路更加燥<br />\n心急既我完全唔明點解啲支那人咁鐘意行行下停係馬路中心周圍望<br />\n更唔明點解要隔住十九幾個人咁傾計<br />\n所以想集思廣益有咩方法對付呢班煩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我先拋磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n地鐵柱女: 㩒9住佢啲頭髮<br />\n比喼碌過: 一下踢返佢個喼<br />\n比支那人撞9開: 踩佢鞋踭<br />\n<br />\n不過其實最有用 都係擰轉頭講句屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf88353558e0c179bb3b6e752f6f98816dc7fcc9","tid":871482,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:49:10.000Z","msg":"一見到阻住自己我就踢喼<br />\n<br />\n問路十問十唔應 或者俾條錯路"},{"pid":"9e145eec439060bbc6adb76d06c678d9599c65a8","tid":871482,"uid":20845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T05:11:16.000Z","msg":"一野踢佢個喼上地鐵<br />\n阻撚住哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247d90efdd083c55e092cba491d222f9d90597ac","tid":871482,"uid":82521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf88353558e0c179bb3b6e752f6f98816dc7fcc9","tid":871482,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:49:10.000Z","msg":"一見到阻住自己我就踢喼<br />\n<br />\n問路十問十唔應 或者俾條錯路"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:24:22.000Z","msg":"近排鐘意直行直過 見支那人橫cut照踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}